exports[`documentation plugin > snapshot: full representative schema output > models/Post.md 1`] = `
"[Index](../index.md)

# Post

> A blog post.

**Category:** Content

**Defined in:** \`../../../../../tmp/zenstack-schema-46c83599-5f3d-4a61-bc5c-eee1bf1198ba.zmodel\`

## Fields

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Attributes | Source | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| id | String | Yes | \`cuid()\` | \`@id\` | — |  |
| title | String | Yes | — | — | — | The post title. |
| content | String? | No | — | — | — |  |
| author | [User](./User.md) | Yes | — | \`@relation(fields: [authorId], references: [id])\` | — |  |
| authorId | String | Yes | — | — | — |  |

## Relationships

| Field | Related Model | Type |
| --- | --- | --- |
| author | [User](./User.md) | Many→One |

## Declaration

\`\`\`prisma
/// A blog post.
            model Post {
                id       String @id @default(cuid())
                /// The post title.
                title    String
                content  String?
                author   User   @relation(fields: [authorId], references: [id])
                authorId String

                @@meta('doc:category', 'Content')
            }
\`\`\`
"
`;

