"[Index](../index.md)

# User

> Represents a registered user.

**Category:** Identity

**Since:** 1.0

**Defined in:** \`../../../../../tmp/zenstack-schema-46c83599-5f3d-4a61-bc5c-eee1bf1198ba.zmodel\`

## Fields

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Attributes | Source | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| id | String | Yes | \`cuid()\` | \`@id\` | — |  |
| email | String | Yes | — | \`@unique\`, \`@email\` | — | User's email address. |
| name | String | Yes | — | — | — | Display name shown in the UI. |
| role | [Role](../enums/Role.md) | Yes | — | — | — |  |
| posts | [Post](./Post.md)[] | No | — | — | — |  |

## Relationships

| Field | Related Model | Type |
| --- | --- | --- |
| posts | [Post](./Post.md) | One→Many |

## Access Policies

| Operation | Rule | Effect |
| --- | --- | --- |
| read | \`true\` | Allow |
| delete | \`true\` | Deny |

## Indexes

| Fields | Type |
| --- | --- |
| \`[email]\` | Index |

## Validation Rules

| Field | Rule |
| --- | --- |
| email | \`@email\` |

## Declaration

\`\`\`prisma
/// Represents a registered user.
            model User {
                id    String @id @default(cuid())
                /// User's email address.
                email String @unique @email
                /// Display name shown in the UI.
                name  String
                role  Role
                posts Post[]

                @@allow('read', true)
                @@deny('delete', true)
                @@index([email])
                @@meta('doc:category', 'Identity')
                @@meta('doc:since', '1.0')
            }
\`\`\`
"
`;

